    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🧹Data Cleaning\n\n**Purpose**\nCleans raw leads automatically in the background. Takes messy scraped data from `staging_leads`, fixes it, removes duplicates, and moves good leads into `cleaned_leads`.\n\n**How it works**\nRuns every **15 minutes** → picks up to 50 pending leads → cleans emails and phone numbers → checks for duplicates → inserts new leads into `cleaned_leads` → marks staging lead as done.\n\n**Key Rules**\n- Leads with **no email AND no phone** are dropped\n- Duplicate check is based on email or phone match\n- Runs fully automatically nothing to trigger manually",
        "height": 496,
        "width": 304
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -4912,
        832
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "a229e8e6-d3d1-48c5-81b9-b5a2f13f49e1",
      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "hours"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        -4912,
        1392
      ],
      "id": "23e14763-b511-4eea-9ea1-9fa56ad26975",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger"
    },
